description:
This is some of the data used to qualify the  NEBNext&reg; Multiplex Oligos for Illumina (Unique Dual Index UMI Adaptors RNA Set 1) . 
 Libraries were prepared from 100 ng of UHR RNA (Agilent) using the  NEBNext Ultra II Directional RNA Library Prep Kit &nbsp;with  ribosomal depletion . 
 &nbsp;

